  <h1>The Verdant Sentinel: A Journey Through Time with the Hamilton Khaki Field</h1>
  <div class="story-category">Hamilton</div>
  <div class="story-meta-line"><span>Story</span><span>•</span><span>~443.83 USD</span></div>
